sentences.english: Many major state universities doubled or tripled their enrollments in one or two years.
sentences.chinese: 許多主要州立大學的入學人數在一兩年內翻了兩三倍。

sentences.english: She teaches in a state university.
sentences.chinese: 她在一所州立大學任教。

sentences.english: She graduated with Master degree in major vocal pedagogy from Northeaster Illinois University in 2007.
sentences.chinese: 現獲得東北伊利諾州立大學聲樂教學法碩士學位。

sentences.english: I have also added a Psychology certification through Emporia State University.
sentences.chinese: 同時我還通過了伯恩利亞州立大學的心理學認證。

sentences.english: Mr. Karras, a doctoral student in education at Ohio State.
sentences.chinese: 在俄亥俄州立大學攻讀教育學博士的卡拉斯先生。

sentences.english: That long summer in 1971, I was at Illinois State University of USA.
sentences.chinese: 一九七一年的夏天，我在美國伊利諾州立大學。

sentences.english: She obtained the TESL Certificate issued by the California State University.
sentences.chinese: 獲美國加州州立大學國際英語TESL培訓證書。

sentences.english: Wayne State University in Detroit had a really great BFA theater program.
sentences.chinese: 底特律的韋恩州立大學有非常棒的BFA戲劇課程。

sentences.english: NC State's Department of Chemical and Biomolecular Engineering is part of the university's College of Engineering.
sentences.chinese: NC州立大學生化工程部屬於該校工程院。

sentences.english: Pretty soon after studying some time in the university of Michigan Madonna wanted to go to New York to chase her dreams.
sentences.chinese: 在密歇根州立大學學習不久，麥當娜想到紐約尋夢。

sentences.english: So she started teaching a class at Portland State University.
sentences.chinese: 因此，她開始在波特蘭州立大學教課。

sentences.english: At the University of Minnesota, a computer algorithm paired people up.
sentences.chinese: 在密尼蘇達州立大學，通過計算機算法將同學分組。

sentences.english: She attended Jackson State University and got a BSW (Bachelor of Social Work).
sentences.chinese: 她在傑克遜州立大學獲得了社會服務學本科學位。

sentences.english: He was educated at Iowa State University and the University of Nebraska.
sentences.chinese: 在艾荷華州立大學及尼布拉斯加大學受教育。

sentences.english: All finds will be passed to the archaeology museum of Karaganda State University.
sentences.chinese: 所有的發現將會被送至卡拉幹達州立大學考古博物館。

sentences.english: This is the website for Department of Plant Pathology at Michigan State University.
sentences.chinese: 這是密歇根州立大學植物病理學系的網站。
